{"tid":757513,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「真人真事」今日打籃波比mk妹拎對波撞我","createTime":"2018-07-27T02:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T02:55:07.000Z","uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"584fa403e87bc8988a239f8fa513af67c335ff14","tid":757513,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:19:33.000Z","msg":"今日無撚聊走落街場射下波啦<br />\n<br />\n射射下有兩條mk妹走咗過黎睇<br />\n<br />\n跟住其中一個mk妹話：條仔射波幾型wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我聽到之後笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢地仲問可唔可以一齊打<br />\n<br />\n咁我都無所謂啦，打波jer又唔係打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開頭都無乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n點知我準備射果時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個mk妹拎對波撞鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我即刻趴咗響地下<br />\n<br />\n條mk妹即刻跑過黎問我有無事，係咁say sorry<br />\n<br />\n之後仲留埋電話比我話想請我食飯賠罪<br />\n<br />\n另一條mk妹就幫我做人工呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下我應該點做？應唔應約好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：條女應該有D，唔係應該撞唔低我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b4f4d95a3d701402f31a9215ea441a729584cc","tid":757513,"uid":78813,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"584fa403e87bc8988a239f8fa51